Title: CM meets Governor
Content: Chief Minister N. Chandrababu Naidu met Governor E.S.L. Narasimhan here on Wednesday after the latter took part in the Krishna Pushkaram festivities at Punnami Ghat and had darshan of goddess Kanaka D
